TopicTitle: A Neil Armstrong Tribute - A YouTube Video

Articles.Content:
Well guys here is one of my Lets Plays on KSP. I thought it fitting to land on the Mun and return to honor the great man that is Neil Armstrong. I recorded and uploaded this a while back and I'm only posting it now as i have just got a forum account. Enjoy

If you enjoyed don't be afraid to check out my other KSP vids or indeed any of my other series. Im relatively new to the youtube scene so if you have any feedback i would be grateful. Also dont forget to "like" if you did or throw me a sub if you want to keep up to date with all my vids

Peace.

Rabid out.
